						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Date: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>A figure of trident is depicted in the middle of this inscription, which records that the lake Aṉṟilēri is stated be the <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> gift of the temple of Peruntirukkōyiluḍaiyār.</p>						

						<p>This epigraph on the grounds of palaeography may be assigned to the 14th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
